call.sql: SELECT DISTINCT t1.DOCUMENT_INSTANCE_ID, t1.ENTITY_NAME, t1.DOCUMENT_TYPE, t1.SEQUENCE_NUMBER, t1.STATUS, t1.LAST_UPDATE_DATE, t1.ENTITY_ID, t0.DELIVERY_LEG_ID, t0.DELIVERY_ID, t2.DELIVERY_ID DeliveryDetailID, t2."NAME" DeliveryName, t2.STATUS_CODE DeliveryStatus, t2.CONFIRM_DATE, t2.SHIPMENT_DIRECTION, t2.ORGANIZATION_ID, t3.SHORT_CODE, t4.ROW_ID, t4.TRIP_ID, t4."NAME", t4.PLANNED_FLAG, t4.STATUS_NAME, t4.VEHICLE_NUMBER, t4.SHIP_METHOD_CODE FROM WSH_DOCUMENT_INSTANCES t1 LEFT OUTER JOIN WSH_DELIVERY_LEGS t0 ON (t0.DELIVERY_LEG_ID = t1.ENTITY_ID) LEFT OUTER JOIN WSH_NEW_DELIVERIES t2 ON (t2.DELIVERY_ID = t0.DELIVERY_ID) LEFT OUTER JOIN HR_OPERATING_UNITS t3 ON (t3.ORGANIZATION_ID = t2.ORGANIZATION_ID) LEFT OUTER JOIN WSH_DELIVERY_TRIPS_V t4 ON (t4.DELIVERY_ID = t2.DELIVERY_ID) WHERE t1.DOCUMENT_TYPE = NVL(#DocumentType,t1.DOCUMENT_TYPE) AND t1.STATUS =NVL(#Status,t1.STATUS) AND t1.SEQUENCE_NUMBER = NVL(#DocumentNumber,t1.SEQUENCE_NUMBER) AND t2.ORGANIZATION_ID = NVL(#OrganizationId,t2.ORGANIZATION_ID) AND t3.SHORT_CODE = NVL(#OrganizationCode,t3.SHORT_CODE) ORDER BY t1.creation_date DESC FETCH FIRST nvl(#rowNum,10) row only
